text: Midland Junction may refer to: *Midland Junction, Indiana, an unincorporated community in Greene County, Indiana **The rail junction of the Monon Railroad I&L; branch and the Chicago Milwaukee St Paul and Pacific Railroad at Midland Junction, Indiana *Midland Junction A former name of Midland, Western Australia **Midland Junction railway station, a former railway station in Midland, Western Australia **Midland Junction Football Club, a defunct Australian rules football club that played in the West Australian Football League *Town of Midland Junction, former name of the Town of Midland, a defunct municipality now part of the City of Swan
title: Midland Junction (disambiguation)
